      <action-date date="20131121">November 21, 2013</action-date>
      <action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S354">Ms. Baldwin</sponsor> (for herself and <cosponsor name-id="S303">Mr. Thune</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSFI00">Committee on Finance</committee-name>
